- D: Blurring the sharp contrast the passage has drawn, This phrase suggests a different rhetorical relationship than the one required between the two clauses.', NULL, 'Expression of Ideas', 'Transitions', 'reading_writing', 'expression', 'TRA', NULL, 'hard', false, 'SAT', 'multiple_choice', true, true, 'scholaris_ai', '{"rw_subtype":"transition","rw_format":"transition_blank","dsat_blueprint_v1":true,"dsat_topic":"science","generator":"generate-dsat-rw-expansion.mjs","explanation_v2":true,"blueprint_version":"dsat_blueprint_v1","challenged_problem":true,"difficulty_tier":"challenged","original":true}'::jsonb, now(), now())
